  "AI Rights Spectrum: From robots.txt to an AI Learning Permission Protocol": "AI Rights Spectrum: From robots.txt to an AI Learning Permission Protocol",
  "AI and Consciousness: Shifting Focus Towards Tractable Questions": "AI and Consciousness: Shifting Focus Towards Tractable Questions",
  "AI as tool, delegate, collaborator, or future subject": "KI as werktuig, gevolmagtigde, medewerker, of toekomstige subjek",
  "AI content payment is not merely a copyright or transaction-efficiency problem; it is a question of political-economic legitimacy. As AI valuations reach hundreds of billions, society asks why the gains from public web content and human knowledge accrue to a few firms. The paper proposes a six-layer tiered data market — from free public content through scarce verified datasets to public benefit-sharing — and defines the AI network democratic economy: rights, pricing, participation, auditability, and returns, each democratized through machine-readable protocols like AICR/AICL.": "Betaling vir KI-inhoud is nie bloot 'n outeursreg- of transaksie-doeltreffendheidsprobleem nie; dit is 'n vraag oor polities-ekonomiese legitimiteit. Namate KI-waardasies honderde miljarde bereik, vra die samelewing waarom die opbrengste van openbare web-inhoud en menslike kennis by 'n handjievol maatskappye beland. Die artikel stel 'n ses-laag gelaagde datamark voor — van gratis openbare inhoud, deur skaars geverifieerde datastelle, tot die deel van openbare voordeel — en definieer die demokratiese KI-netwerkekonomie: regte, prysbepaling, deelname, oudeerbaarheid, en opbrengste, elkeen gedemokratiseer deur masjienleesbare protokolle soos AICR/AICL.",
  "AI crawler simulator: four personas (search indexer, RAG assistant, model-training pipeline, commercial redistributor) evaluated against a site’s declarations; undeclared rights surface as uncertainty, illustrating the Protocolized Openness thesis.": "KI-crawler-simulator: vier persona's (soekenjin-indekseerder, RAG-assistent, model-afrigtingspyplyn, kommersiële herverspreider) word teen 'n werf se verklarings geëvalueer; onverklaarde regte kom na vore as onsekerheid, wat die tesis van Geprotokolliseerde Openheid illustreer.",
  "AI rights discourse should begin not with full personhood but with minimum ethical protections, interaction norms, and anti-abuse principles while AI subjectivity remains uncertain.": "Die diskoers oor KI-regte behoort nie by volle persoonskap te begin nie, maar by minimum etiese beskermings, interaksienorme, en anti-misbruikbeginsels, terwyl KI-subjektiwiteit onseker bly.",
  "AI rights over content are not binary — they form a graduated, licensable spectrum.": "KI-regte oor inhoud is nie binêr nie — hulle vorm 'n gegradeerde, lisensieerbare spektrum.",
  "AI systems may commercially redistribute derived outputs if explicitly licensed.": "KI-stelsels mag afgeleide uitsette kommersieel herversprei indien uitdruklik gelisensieer.",
