  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Kodevoorbeelde, JSON-skemas, en masjienleesbare beleidsjablone word onder die MIT-lisensie gelisensieer, tensy anders vermeld. U mag dit vrylik op u eie werwe ontplooi.",
