  "Correct positioning: independent research drafts, protocol proposals, and an open specification experiment.": "Korrekte posisionering: onafhanklike navorsingskonsepte, protokolvoorstelle, en 'n eksperiment in oop spesifikasies.",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Belgium (BE) now maps to Dutch instead of French — Flemish speakers are the country’s majority (~60%) over Walloon French speakers (~40%).": "'n Vroeëre verstekwaarde reggestel: België (BE) skakel nou na Nederlands in plaas van Frans — Vlaamssprekendes is die land se meerderheid (~60%) teenoor Waalse Franssprekendes (~40%).",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Kazakhstan (KZ) now maps to Kazakh instead of Russian, now that a Kazakh translation exists — the same kind of fix as the earlier Belgium correction.": "'n Vroeëre verstekwaarde reggestel: Kasakstan (KZ) skakel nou na Kasak in plaas van Russies, noudat 'n Kasak-vertaling bestaan — dieselfde soort regstelling as die vroeëre België-korreksie.",
  "Could AI Be Conscious?": "Could AI Be Conscious?",
